URGENT
CONVENIENCE STORE STAFF NEEDED

536
00:58:55,239 --> 00:58:56,920
You already look handsome, sir.

537
00:58:57,400 --> 00:58:58,679
Time for work.

538
00:59:01,360 --> 00:59:04,960
Are you coming
to that village with us tonight?

539
00:59:05,639 --> 00:59:07,119
Laddaland Village?

540
00:59:07,800 --> 00:59:10,960
Damn that creepy place.
You still dare to go?

541
00:59:11,360 --> 00:59:14,800
Right. Only the idiots still live there.

542
00:59:15,199 --> 00:59:16,880
Go right ahead.

543
00:59:17,119 --> 00:59:19,280
I hope you find what you're looking for.

544
00:59:25,039 --> 00:59:26,000
Hey!

545
00:59:26,119 --> 00:59:27,320
Shit!

546
00:59:31,079 --> 00:59:32,960
-Hey!
-Let me go!

547
00:59:35,199 --> 00:59:36,360
Hey, I need help.

548
00:59:36,880 --> 00:59:37,840
Hey, stop!

549
00:59:40,599 --> 00:59:41,679
What's wrong with you?

550
00:59:41,880 --> 00:59:43,360
How could you do that to the customer?

551
00:59:43,559 --> 00:59:44,719
He was shoplifting!

552
00:59:44,800 --> 00:59:46,159
Just call the police!

553
00:59:46,320 --> 00:59:49,440
This is unacceptable.
Leave now. You're fired!

554
00:59:50,079 --> 00:59:51,079
I'm not leaving!

555
00:59:53,000 --> 00:59:54,360
If I go, how the hell will I live?

556
01:00:12,239 --> 01:00:13,239
SAVINGS DEPOSIT PASSBOOK

557
01:00:46,039 --> 01:00:47,000
What's that voice?

558
01:00:50,000 --> 01:00:51,119
Golf, what are you doing?

559
01:00:55,840 --> 01:00:57,239
Nat, come here.

560
01:01:00,280 --> 01:01:01,480
What were you guys playing, Golf?

561
01:01:01,719 --> 01:01:03,079
What if something happened to him?

562
01:01:04,719 --> 01:01:07,719
He hid inside the closet.

563
01:01:08,639 --> 01:01:10,000
I was just joking with him.

564
01:01:10,079 --> 01:01:11,159
Joking?

565
01:01:11,760 --> 01:01:14,000
If you are going to play like this,
then don't play here anymore.

566
01:01:14,079 --> 01:01:15,159
Go home now.

567
01:01:26,199 --> 01:01:28,159
Your son locked my son inside the closet.

568
01:01:28,400 --> 01:01:30,320
What would happen if nobody was home?

569
01:01:34,119 --> 01:01:34,960
Golf.

570
01:01:39,119 --> 01:01:40,360
Did you do that to his son?

571
01:01:47,039 --> 01:01:47,920
Satisfied?

572
01:01:50,559 --> 01:01:51,480
Go inside.

573
01:02:01,719 --> 01:02:03,480
LADDALAND

574
01:03:30,880 --> 01:03:31,800
Parn.

575
01:03:32,599 --> 01:03:33,519
Parn!

576
01:03:34,199 --> 01:03:35,360
-Parn!
-Yes?

577
01:03:35,599 --> 01:03:36,440
Where is Nat?

578
01:03:36,559 --> 01:03:37,760
He went to play outside with Golf.

579
01:03:50,800 --> 01:03:52,119
Nat!

580
01:04:14,639 --> 01:04:15,559
Nat!

581
01:04:20,280 --> 01:04:21,199
Nat!

582
01:04:22,960 --> 01:04:23,840
Nat!

583
01:04:29,119 --> 01:04:30,039
Nat!

584
01:04:32,960 --> 01:04:34,079
Nat, is that you?

585
01:05:16,400 --> 01:05:17,320
Nat, is that you?

586
01:05:32,719 --> 01:05:33,559
Hello, Parn.

587
01:05:33,639 --> 01:05:35,679
Hello, Thee. Where are you now?

588
01:05:36,079 --> 01:05:37,199
Nat is already home.

589
01:05:58,639 --> 01:06:00,599
Why did you play
inside that foreigner's house?

590
01:06:01,559 --> 01:06:03,280
Answer me.
Why did you play inside that house?

591
01:06:03,360 --> 01:06:06,519
Golf told me to go get Chowguay.

592
01:06:15,840 --> 01:06:17,480
Your son is too much now!

593
01:06:20,000 --> 01:06:21,840
He forced my son to go
inside that foreigner's house.

594
01:06:22,000 --> 01:06:23,960
What are you going to do
if something happened to my son?

595
01:06:24,039 --> 01:06:24,880
Has anything happened?

596
01:06:25,519 --> 01:06:27,039
How dare you say that?

597
01:06:29,159 --> 01:06:30,079
Are you done?

598
01:06:31,559 --> 01:06:33,079
What kind of a father are you?

599
01:06:33,239 --> 01:06:35,480
If you can't teach your own son
then just call him out here.

600
01:06:35,559 --> 01:06:36,679
I will teach him in your place!

601
01:06:36,800 --> 01:06:38,639
I can teach my own son.

602
01:06:40,199 --> 01:06:41,400
You go tell your wife

603
01:06:41,519 --> 01:06:43,199
to mind her own business.

604
01:06:43,800 --> 01:06:45,239
Give me back my money first.

605
01:06:45,559 --> 01:06:46,760
When did I ever borrow your money?

606
01:06:46,880 --> 01:06:49,800
Your wife asked my wife
for 10,000 baht last month.

607
01:07:00,800 --> 01:07:03,079
It's you who can't handle your shit.

608
01:07:03,360 --> 01:07:05,760
If you're damn proud,
take care of your family with your money.

609
01:07:06,559 --> 01:07:08,320
Why do you have to bother others?

610
01:07:14,119 --> 01:07:15,239
Here's your money!

611
01:07:16,880 --> 01:07:18,280
And keep out of our business!

612
01:07:31,280 --> 01:07:32,719
Damn cat!

613
01:09:18,079 --> 01:09:19,000
Excuse me?

614
01:09:19,880 --> 01:09:21,399
I'm ready to pay.

615
01:09:21,479 --> 01:09:22,720
Oh, okay.

616
01:09:29,399 --> 01:09:30,560
Do you want some more sausages?

617
01:09:36,840 --> 01:09:37,760
How much?

618
01:09:40,680 --> 01:09:41,680
Twelve baht.

619
01:09:44,520 --> 01:09:45,560
Keep the change.

620
01:10:23,039 --> 01:10:24,319
Why didn't you tell me?

621
01:10:25,159 --> 01:10:26,479
How would it help if I told you?

622
01:10:27,239 --> 01:10:29,079
Is it any better to keep it to yourself?

623
01:10:32,159 --> 01:10:34,039
I have a job interview
the day after tomorrow.

624
01:10:35,720 --> 01:10:37,279
I just need to borrow the money for now.

625
01:10:38,000 --> 01:10:39,760
I will put it back when I get paid.

626
01:10:47,039 --> 01:10:48,560
I am going back to work.

627
01:10:48,960 --> 01:10:51,239
Mr. Manop has opened a new branch here
in Chiang Mai.

628
01:10:58,840 --> 01:11:00,600
You want to go back to work
or go back to him?

629
01:11:55,039 --> 01:11:57,560
You used to do marketing in Bangkok
for about ten years.

630
01:11:57,760 --> 01:12:01,479
It should be easy for you to expand
the market for us here.

631
01:12:01,840 --> 01:12:05,560
Actually, different people
in different locations

632
01:12:05,640 --> 01:12:07,840
have different natures
that will vary accordingly.

633
01:12:08,159 --> 01:12:10,199
From my experience,

634
01:12:10,279 --> 01:12:12,319
my marketing strategy would be...

635
01:12:14,159 --> 01:12:15,199
I'm sorry.

636
01:12:18,960 --> 01:12:21,560
From my experience,

637
01:12:21,640 --> 01:12:24,479
any time we want to change the consumers

638
01:12:24,560 --> 01:12:27,000
or change the consumers' habits

639
01:12:27,079 --> 01:12:28,960
we should...

640
01:12:29,760 --> 01:12:30,680
I'm sorry.

641
01:12:30,880 --> 01:12:32,920
There must be some emergency at home.

642
01:12:34,760 --> 01:12:36,960
Parn, I'm having a job interview.

643
01:13:01,760 --> 01:13:02,920
Mr. Thee.

644
01:13:03,000 --> 01:13:05,439
Mr. Somkiat shot everyone in the house.

645
01:13:05,880 --> 01:13:09,079
He was probably stressed about work.

646
01:13:09,239 --> 01:13:11,840
His factory went bankrupt
with ten million baht in debt.

647
01:13:12,439 --> 01:13:15,640
It's true. Nid borrowed money
from so many people.

648
01:13:16,199 --> 01:13:19,039
Did she ask you too?
I thought she only asked me.

649
01:13:19,359 --> 01:13:20,880
Me too.

650
01:13:21,520 --> 01:13:23,520
I am reporting a homicide.

651
01:13:23,600 --> 01:13:27,760
One male, two females,
one boy at Laddaland Village.

652
01:13:28,399 --> 01:13:29,600
Poor Golf.

653
01:13:29,680 --> 01:13:32,520
Someone said his skull caved in
where he was shot.

654
01:13:35,359 --> 01:13:37,319
Didn't you hear anything, Mr. Thee?

655
01:13:37,800 --> 01:13:40,680
Mr. Somkiat has been dead
in that house for days.

656
01:13:44,000 --> 01:13:45,600
I don't want to live here anymore.

657
01:13:46,520 --> 01:13:48,319
- Let's move out.
- Where will we move to?

658
01:13:48,760 --> 01:13:50,000
Our home is here.

659
01:13:52,960 --> 01:13:54,439
I'm about to get a new job.

660
01:13:55,680 --> 01:13:57,039
Everything will get better.

661
01:13:58,079 --> 01:13:59,920
It is not about work anymore, Thee.

662
01:14:01,600 --> 01:14:02,840
Didn't you see?

663
01:14:04,000 --> 01:14:06,039
They have been dead for days.

664
01:14:06,479 --> 01:14:09,039
-That means the last few days--
-It was just all in our heads.

665
01:14:12,319 --> 01:14:13,520
Pack up.

666
01:14:13,960 --> 01:14:15,239
Let's go back to Bangkok.

667
01:14:15,800 --> 01:14:17,039
Let's start over.

668
01:14:17,720 --> 01:14:18,920
It's easy to say that, Parn.

669
01:14:19,680 --> 01:14:21,119
But we still have to pay off this house.

670
01:14:21,600 --> 01:14:22,960
If we move now,

671
01:14:23,560 --> 01:14:24,960
I will lose the house

672
01:14:25,319 --> 01:14:26,680
and the installments.

673
01:14:28,199 --> 01:14:29,359
What would I have left?

674
01:14:37,159 --> 01:14:38,760
You have me and the kids.

675
01:14:39,600 --> 01:14:42,960
Weren't we happy back then,
even when we didn't have our own house?

676
01:14:51,920 --> 01:14:54,159
I don't want to go back
so your mom can look down on me.

677
01:14:57,840 --> 01:15:00,680
You care how she feels about you.

678
01:15:00,960 --> 01:15:03,560
But don't you care
how the kids and I feel?

679
01:15:03,880 --> 01:15:05,159
I don't care, Parn?

680
01:15:06,279 --> 01:15:08,319
Who do you think
I'm doing all of this for?

681
01:15:09,119 --> 01:15:12,359
I bought this house for you and our kids.

682
01:15:13,600 --> 01:15:15,439
So we can all be together.

683
01:15:16,800 --> 01:15:18,159
Is this "not caring," Parn?

684
01:15:23,399 --> 01:15:24,560
Let's go back to Bangkok.

685
01:15:26,600 --> 01:15:30,680
If we can't afford a house,
we can rent like before.

686
01:15:30,880 --> 01:15:32,279
And Nan will stay with us.

687
01:15:32,880 --> 01:15:34,000
I will help.

688
01:15:34,800 --> 01:15:36,239
I will go back to work.

689
01:15:38,520 --> 01:15:39,920
Do you want to go back to work that bad?

690
01:15:40,439 --> 01:15:43,479
You keep nagging me about going to Bangkok
because you want to see him, right?

691
01:15:45,399 --> 01:15:47,680
Hey, wait. Listen to me carefully.

692
01:15:48,279 --> 01:15:51,560
How many times do I have to tell you
that Mr. Manop is just my boss.

693
01:15:51,640 --> 01:15:52,520
Just your boss?

694
01:15:53,720 --> 01:15:55,720
Why did he come all the way here
in Chiang Mai?

695
01:15:55,840 --> 01:15:58,399
And so? I wasn't the one who went to him!

696
01:15:58,640 --> 01:16:00,560
Who comes or goes isn't the point.

697
01:16:01,479 --> 01:16:02,720
The point is,

698
01:16:03,319 --> 01:16:04,439
what were you two doing?

699
01:16:09,239 --> 01:16:12,159
I will try to believe that
you are saying all of this

700
01:16:12,560 --> 01:16:13,920
because you are angry.

701
01:16:15,680 --> 01:16:17,960
But if you really think that
I am that kind of person,

702
01:16:18,880 --> 01:16:20,119
we can't live together anymore.

703
01:18:40,279 --> 01:18:42,680
FOR SALE

704
01:19:26,399 --> 01:19:30,479
LADDALAND

705
01:19:47,640 --> 01:19:48,520
Nat!

706
01:19:48,960 --> 01:19:50,399
Nat! Come down right now!

707
01:19:53,359 --> 01:19:56,159
How many times did I tell you
to put your toys away?

708
01:19:56,239 --> 01:19:57,560
I didn't take them out.

709
01:19:57,640 --> 01:19:59,319
So I did then?

710
01:20:00,319 --> 01:20:02,039
Golf did.

711
01:20:04,239 --> 01:20:05,119
Nat.

712
01:20:05,199 --> 01:20:06,319
Don't lie to me.

713
01:20:06,600 --> 01:20:08,680
They all went to Bangkok
and they are not home.

714
01:20:08,880 --> 01:20:10,119
They already came back.

715
01:20:10,199 --> 01:20:12,479
We are playing hide and seek now.

716
01:20:15,720 --> 01:20:17,520
Don't lie to me!
They haven't come back yet!

717
01:20:17,600 --> 01:20:18,560
They did.

718
01:20:18,640 --> 01:20:19,800
Nat, stop lying!

719
01:20:20,039 --> 01:20:21,039
Golf!

720
01:20:21,119 --> 01:20:22,520
-Nat!
-You can come out now!

721
01:20:22,600 --> 01:20:23,880
I don't want to play anymore!

722
01:20:23,960 --> 01:20:25,640
-Nat!
-Please come out!

723
01:20:25,720 --> 01:20:26,840
Golf.

724
01:20:27,119 --> 01:20:29,840
Golf, I don't want to play anymore.
Come out.

725
01:20:29,920 --> 01:20:34,880
Golf, come out already.
I don't want to play anymore.

726
01:20:35,239 --> 01:20:36,479
Golf!

727
01:20:39,199 --> 01:20:40,039
Nat!

728
01:20:40,119 --> 01:20:41,760
Golf, I don't want to play anymore.

729
01:20:46,560 --> 01:20:48,399
Golf, come out now.

730
01:20:53,000 --> 01:20:54,560
-Nat!
-Golf!

731
01:20:54,640 --> 01:20:56,239
My mom is yelling at me!

732
01:20:56,960 --> 01:21:00,680
Golf. I don't want to play anymore.
Come out.

733
01:21:01,479 --> 01:21:02,479
Golf!

734
01:21:05,000 --> 01:21:06,840
Enough. Stop lying to me!

735
01:21:06,920 --> 01:21:08,520
I'm not lying.

736
01:21:08,880 --> 01:21:10,680
Nat. Don't lie to me!

737
01:21:10,760 --> 01:21:12,399
I didn't lie.

738
01:21:12,479 --> 01:21:14,159
I told you to stop!

739
01:21:14,239 --> 01:21:15,680
I'm not lying.

740
01:21:15,760 --> 01:21:17,119
So what were you doing just now?

741
01:21:17,199 --> 01:21:19,079
I'm not lying!

742
01:21:19,159 --> 01:21:21,039
You said Golf is here. Where is he?

743
01:21:21,479 --> 01:21:23,359
I guess he already went home.

744
01:21:23,439 --> 01:21:26,399
That's not true. Nat, don't lie to me.
Stop lying to me!

745
01:21:26,600 --> 01:21:28,479
I'm not lying.

746
01:21:28,640 --> 01:21:30,479
Why are you a bad child?

747
01:21:30,560 --> 01:21:32,760
Why are you a bad child?

748
01:21:32,960 --> 01:21:35,279
Didn't I already tell you?

749
01:21:35,600 --> 01:21:37,920
Why? Stop it!

750
01:21:38,000 --> 01:21:39,720
Stop crying now!

751
01:21:39,800 --> 01:21:41,119
-Parn!
-Stop!

752
01:21:41,199 --> 01:21:42,039
-Parn!
-Stop crying!

753
01:21:42,119 --> 01:21:42,960
-Parn!
-Stop!

754
01:21:43,680 --> 01:21:44,960
Why are you hitting him?

755
01:21:46,159 --> 01:21:47,560
Are you out of your mind?

756
01:21:49,319 --> 01:21:50,479
What's wrong with you?

757
01:22:27,880 --> 01:22:29,279
Goodness, am I dreaming?

758
01:22:29,840 --> 01:22:32,159
I'm honored that
you are actually calling me first.

759
01:22:35,319 --> 01:22:36,199
Mom...

760
01:22:42,520 --> 01:22:43,520
It's okay.

761
01:22:46,880 --> 01:22:48,560
Even if I hate your husband's guts,

762
01:22:49,359 --> 01:22:50,920
you are still my daughter.

763
01:22:51,640 --> 01:22:53,039
And I love my grandkids.

764
01:22:54,199 --> 01:22:57,439
If you can't stand staying there anymore,
feel free to move back here.

765
01:22:58,399 --> 01:23:01,239
I can tolerate looking at your husband
once or twice a week.

766
01:23:01,319 --> 01:23:04,479
It's better than seeing you
and my grandkids haunted by ghosts.

767
01:23:05,000 --> 01:23:06,680
Do you want me to talk to him?

768
01:23:07,319 --> 01:23:08,399
That's okay, Mom.

769
01:23:08,880 --> 01:23:10,600
I will talk to him tomorrow.

770
01:23:58,920 --> 01:23:59,760
Nan,

771
01:23:59,960 --> 01:24:02,239
pack up. We're going back to Bangkok.

772
01:24:52,920 --> 01:24:54,039
Excuse me.

773
01:24:55,880 --> 01:24:57,199
Is anyone home?

774
01:26:11,479 --> 01:26:12,640
I'm sorry.

775
01:26:25,760 --> 01:26:27,279
EMERGENCY ROOM

776
01:26:28,479 --> 01:26:30,119
Please calm down.

777
01:26:30,199 --> 01:26:31,600
Please stay calm.

778
01:26:33,159 --> 01:26:34,720
There's nothing there.

779
01:26:35,319 --> 01:26:36,680
Nat, please stay here.

780
01:26:45,119 --> 01:26:46,000
Parn.

781
01:26:47,880 --> 01:26:48,720
Parn.

782
01:26:50,039 --> 01:26:51,560
Go away. Leave me alone.

783
01:26:53,960 --> 01:26:56,239
Do you love that house so much?

784
01:26:57,199 --> 01:26:58,680
Do you love it that much?

785
01:26:59,279 --> 01:27:01,199
How about your kid? Look!

786
01:27:02,960 --> 01:27:05,560
If you love that place that much,
then just go back and live with it.

787
01:27:08,840 --> 01:27:11,000
Nan is so damn unlucky
to have a dad like you!

788
01:27:12,119 --> 01:27:13,840
Go to hell!

789
01:27:17,640 --> 01:27:19,199
-Parn
-Go!

790
01:28:40,479 --> 01:28:41,600
Dad,

791
01:28:43,079 --> 01:28:44,960
can you sleep with me tonight?

792
01:28:47,039 --> 01:28:47,880
Okay, son.

793
01:28:59,399 --> 01:29:00,319
Nat.

794
01:29:01,239 --> 01:29:02,359
Do you like this house?

795
01:29:08,199 --> 01:29:12,399
Yes, but I like our old house more.

796
01:29:53,840 --> 01:29:54,840
Nat.

797
01:29:55,720 --> 01:29:56,640
Nat!

798
01:29:58,720 --> 01:29:59,600
Nat!

799
01:30:00,800 --> 01:30:01,640
